217
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] u duhu i istini mu trebaju.

218
00:12:56,539 --> 00:12:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, braćo i sestre,

219
00:12:57,700 --> 00:13:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] treba održavati tu vatru duha svetoga.

220
00:13:01,659 --> 00:13:05,580
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte još malo da uđemo u to.

221
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:10,580
[SPEAKER_00] Ako u tom hramu ti svječnjaci židovski

222
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:12,779
[SPEAKER_00] sa sedam krakova predstavljaju,

223
00:13:12,779 --> 00:13:14,080
