224
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] koliko mi darova duha svetoga dobijamo?

225
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,759
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ima darova duha svetoga?

226
00:13:19,759 --> 00:13:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sedam darova duha svetoga.

227
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan od njih je pobožnost.

228
00:13:27,039 --> 00:13:29,620
[SPEAKER_00] Pobožnost.

229
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:33,620
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam jesu vam vaše djedovi bake pričali,

230
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:37,080
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja znam jer sam djete sa sela.

231
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:40,100
[SPEAKER_00] Svečenik, kad bi prije išao nositi

232
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] bolesničko pomazanje

233
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:44,379
[SPEAKER_00] i priče s nekome u selu,

234
00:13:44,379 --> 00:13:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] stavio bi štolu,

235
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] išao,

236
00:13:46,799 --> 00:13:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] kogod bi ga ulicom vidio sreo,

237
00:13:49,279 --> 00:13:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] kleknuo bi.

238
00:13:50,059 --> 00:13:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ne svečeniku.

239
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je taj svečenik veći grešnik,

240
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] od tog naroda gdje prolazi.

241
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali narod je znao,

242
00:13:58,159 --> 00:13:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] taj svečenik nosi Isusa.

243
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan plod duha svetoga u meni je pobožnost,

244
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] straho poštovanje pred svetima.

245
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:10,419
[SPEAKER_00] Što se danas je izgubilo?

246
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja gledam na misama, na klanjanjima.

247
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,320
[SPEAKER_00] Neki ne znaju,

248
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,379
[SPEAKER_00] nekim župama kad držim duhovne obnove,

249
00:14:17,379 --> 00:14:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaju kad treba kleknem pred presvjetim.

250
00:14:20,159 --> 00:14:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ustanu stoje, pa ne znaju šta bi.

251
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad mi imamo ove pogrebne mise,

252
00:14:24,779 --> 00:14:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] pa to je ko fitness ovde.

253
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] Sve kontra.

254
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kad treba ustati,

255
00:14:28,019 --> 00:14:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] oni sjednu,

256
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad treba sjest,

257
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] onda ustanu,

258
00:14:30,519 --> 00:14:31,100
[SPEAKER_00] stidi ih,

259
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] jadni ne znaju,

260
00:14:31,779 --> 00:14:32,419
[SPEAKER_00] izgubljeni.

261
00:14:32,419 --> 00:14:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] Gledam vas mlade nekada u crkvi,

262
00:14:34,799 --> 00:14:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] to žlake ovako stane,

263
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,679
