285
00:15:19,259 --> 00:15:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tu vidiš

286
00:15:21,279 --> 00:15:22,740
[SPEAKER_00] da smo olupine.

287
00:15:22,740 --> 00:15:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] Koji hran duha svetoga?

288
00:15:24,519 --> 00:15:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] Koji?

289
00:15:25,779 --> 00:15:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što je Sveti Augustin rekao,

290
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] ok, jesmo materijal,

291
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:33,080
[SPEAKER_00] jesmo kroz sakramente možda oblikovani,

292
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] ali ljubav nije zapalila

293
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] naša srca

294
00:15:37,779 --> 00:15:40,379
[SPEAKER_00] da postanemo hran duha svetoga.

295
00:15:40,379 --> 00:15:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] Zato govorim,

296
00:15:42,779 --> 00:15:45,960
