297
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,620
[SPEAKER_00] ali jednostavno,

298
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno ne dolazi iznutra

299
00:15:51,039 --> 00:15:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] oni plodovi duha svetoga,

300
00:15:53,559 --> 00:15:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] ta vatra,

301
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,379
[SPEAKER_00] ako smo hran duha svetoga.

302
00:15:56,379 --> 00:15:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zato si moramo tu priznat,

303
00:15:58,519 --> 00:16:00,919
[SPEAKER_00] stati pred gospodina

304
00:16:00,919 --> 00:16:01,639
[SPEAKER_00] i reći,

305
00:16:01,639 --> 00:16:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja želim da zaista moje srca

306
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:05,200
[SPEAKER_00] bude ispunjeno

307
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] vatrom duha svetoga.

308
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:07,120
[SPEAKER_00] želim da gorim,

309
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] da budem taj hran.

310
00:16:08,259 --> 00:16:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako gospodin kaže

311
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,460
