565
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to.

566
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] To poželite.

567
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] To poželite.

568
