582
00:23:58,839 --> 00:24:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je ono osjećaj?

583
00:24:00,220 --> 00:24:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom više je na psihu udara.

584
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ali koliko sam se put vidio,

585
00:24:04,700 --> 00:24:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] koliko put sam vidio,

586
