597
00:24:32,119 --> 00:24:36,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je svako klanjenje ovdje duhovna detoksikacija

598
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] i da se svi pročišćavamo.

599
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zato neki vrištimo, neki plaćujemo,

600
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] neki se smijemo, neki šutimo,

601
00:24:42,339 --> 00:24:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali nema veze.

602
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Barem je moving.

603
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] Barem se nešto događa.

604
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] Najgore kad smo kona bara,

605
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] znate kad bara stoji,

606
00:24:52,059 --> 00:24:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] dok nestane s čizmom na nju,

607
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] da se to malo zamuti,

608
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] da one žabe iskoče,

609
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] da sve što je u njoj,

610
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,259
[SPEAKER_00] e, to je to.

611
00:24:58,259 --> 00:25:00,839
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, neka nam gospodin dadne milost

612
00:25:00,839 --> 00:25:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] i duha svetoga da gorimo.

613
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

